277
00:18:55,450 --> 00:18:57,110
Do you want to shower first?

278
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:59,310
- If it's urgent—
- I'll call back later.

279
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:01,290
I'll hang up now.

280
00:19:12,810 --> 00:19:15,910
I can tell there's something going on.

281
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:35,310
Dad! Make it look pretty! Do it again!

282
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:37,820
One, two, three!

283
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:43,780
We should go see the big lighthouse and take the cable car.

284
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:46,210
Just do the cable car. And we'll drive along the coast.

285
00:19:46,210 --> 00:19:47,620
I want to enjoy myself leisurely.

286
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:50,050
I canceled all the plans I made for days because of you.

287
00:19:50,050 --> 00:19:51,340
I don't want to walk!

288
00:19:51,340 --> 00:19:53,220
What's the point of wearing pretty clothes for photos?

289
00:19:53,220 --> 00:19:55,920
You only packed sneakers. Who packed them?

290
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:58,180
Who brings high heels on a trip?

291
00:19:58,180 --> 00:20:00,930
